International:
   Philips, Grundig Video Venture
Under the agreement, Grundig will incorporate its
Nuremberg-based video activities, product development of
videocassette recorders and supporting company functions into
the new venture. Philips will include its entire video
business group, based in Vienna, in the new venture.
   Philips said the two companies don't intend to market
products from the new venture exclusively through existing
trade channels but will offer them through a variety of trade
sources.